Node "Bruce2_2_4_2G_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "*The Explorer stares at you as he wrestles with his conscience. Finally, he gives in to his better nature and visibly sags.* You're right. You're right. I owe you that, Vault Dweller. I wish I'd known your people wouldn't want us snooping around before we left Crossroads."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- MORE -" linkto "Bruce2_2_4_2G_2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Bruce2_2_4_2G_2"
notes "Once the dialogue ends, a script has Bruce and his group of Explorers walking towards the nearest exit grid. They will not appear at V31's entrance again."
{
NPCText "*Bruce runs a hand through his hair and looks at Vault 31's blast door in frustration.* You have no idea how hard it is to walk away from this, Vault Dweller. *He smiles at you.* Don't worry, though. You won't see us around here again. Neither will we tell another soul about this place. Goodbye for now."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye, Bruce. Take care." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Off you go, then." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Bruce2_2_4_3"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Well, then, Vault Dweller, I don't owe you anything. Sooner or later, we're going to get this door open. Are you going to help us?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why do you want to get the door open?" linkto "Bruce2_2_2_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me speak to my people inside. I'll get the door open in no time." linkto "Bruce2_2_3a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll get this door open for you if the price is right." linkto "Bruce2_2_3b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It's a bad idea for you to open that door." linkto "Bruce2_2_3c_1a"  notes "If Bruce has spoken node Bruce2_2_3c_1a before, which means the PC has tried the 'bad idea' path already, go to Bruce2_2_3c_1b instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Clear off, asshole. We don't want your sort poking around here." linkto "Bruce2_B_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Answer me a question, first." linkto "Bruce2_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Bruce2_2_4_4a"
notes "Subtract a scoped hunting rifle and VALUE caps from the PC's inventory. VALUE = 500 - [PC's barter skill *2]. Once the dialogue ends, a script has Bruce and his group of Explorers walking towards the nearest exit grid. They will not appear at V31's entrance again."
{
NPCText "*Bruce takes the rifle and money from you. He takes one last look at Vault 31's huge blast door with a rueful half-smile.* What lies behind that door? *He shakes his head.* I don't know if I've just made a terrible mistake, Vault Dweller. Well, I'll see you around."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Take care, Bruce. Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Just make sure it isn't here." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
