Node "Bruce2_B_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "*Bruce's usually friendly expression goes icy cold. He primes his firearm, whose suggestive click is loud in the cave-like area. Still facing you, he speaks to his team-mates, who stand behind him.* I think we just found the key to this door, fellas."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- MORE -" linkto "Bruce2_B_2"  notes "This one's for the non-dumb path."
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- MORE -" linkto "Bruce2_B_2"  notes "This one's for the dumb path."
