              }
}
Node "Bruce2_B_3a"
notes "I recommend a script which causes the Explorers to attack the PC if he wanders too far away from the door whilst they are expecting him to get it open under this threat of violence."
{
NPCText "Okay. No funny business, I'll be watching you."
      options {
